This functionality can be achieved by using a [Spring Cloud Config Server][1] and a [refresh scope client][2].

**Server**

Server (Spring Boot app) serves the configuration stored, for example, in a Git repository:
&lt;!-- language: lang-java --&gt;

    @SpringBootApplication
    @EnableConfigServer
    public class ConfigServer {
      public static void main(String[] args) {
